            </h1>
            <p class="font-normal text-lg white"></p>
            <br><br>
            <a href="#popupBox"
            class="block bg-white text-black font-bold transition duration-200 shadow hover:shadow-2xl ease-in-and-out rounded-lg mx-auto mt-16 px-2 py-4 text-xl font-sans w-60">
            Add App
            </a>
            <br><br><br>
        </div>
    </div>
        <br>
